      { type: "p", text: "Clear genre positioning Clear fantasy or promise Clear reason to wishlist now" },
      { type: "p", text: "If visitors hesitate, Steam reads that as weak demand." },
      { type: "h3", text: "Amplification: letting Steam see consistency" },
      { type: "p", text: "When traffic comes in bursts that align with engagement, Steam begins to test the game in discovery surfaces. This is where many developers expect magic to happen." },
      { type: "p", text: "But Steam only amplifies what already shows consistency. Not spikes without follow through." },
      { type: "p", text: "A working system connects all three. Traffic sources match the store page message. The store page converts. Steam notices the pattern." },
