      { type: "h2", text: "Step 1: Understand your goals" },
      { type: "p", text: "Before creating a brief for influencers, try to understand what you want to get from this promotion." },
      { type: "h3", text: "What are your KPIs and how are you going to measure them?" },
      { type: "p", text: "Call to action that influencers have to pronounce. Without directly encouraging viewers to complete a very specific action, don't expect to get results. It might sound too promotional while everyone's talking about the organic nature of this type of marketing, but consider that you'll have close to zero results for investments if you don't have a CTA that matches your goal." },
      { type: "p", text: "Tracking of results. It makes sense to think about it in advance - how will you measure whether this integration worked? You can do it through a UTM code or a unique promo code. Don’t forget to add this to the brief." },
      { type: "h3", text: "What message do you want the audience to understand?" },
      { type: "p", text: "This is also called 'message takeaway'. Basically, it's what the audience has to remember after watching your ad. It has to be simple and easy to understand. Can you say it in up to 10 words?" },
