      { type: "h2", text: "The real situation behind an empty wishlist counter" },
      { type: "p", text: "At some point many indie PC developers face the same uncomfortable moment." },
      { type: "p", text: "The Steam page is live. The game is playable or close to it. Updates are happening. People react positively on social platforms or Discord. A few streamers may have tried the game. Traffic exists." },
      { type: "p", text: "Yet the wishlist counter barely moves." },
