      { type: "p", text: "To sum it up, influencers have the power to affect buying decisions because of their authority, expertise, or connection with their followers. Take, for example, the Adidas Members Week Campaign. The company hired 19 Twitch streamers to promote its Members Club, creating special content about it during their streams and on platforms like Discord and X." },
