      { type: "p", text: "Plan your budget and the key performance indicators (KPIs). If you don’t have a large budget but are also not strict in time, consider to mix of mid-size and micro-influencers. This approach can optimize resource allocation while maximizing results." },
      { type: "p", text: "Choose social media platforms that align with your target audience and goals. For instance, platforms like TikTok and Instagram are suited for quick wins, while YouTube can yield long-term results as videos may keep getting views and drive conversions over extended periods." },
